Burger et al. 2010
); epigastric fold with strongly sclerotized lips. Dorsal view: AUS Tshaped structure (Pr), with median part darker, ARe nearly transparent, squared; Pp present, large; posterior recaptulum present, large, egg-shaped membranous sac, apparently connected to base of posterior plate ( Fig. 236- 239 , 262 (arrow)).
